@page "/"
@rendermode InteractiveServer
<PageTitle>BlazorCsvExporter Demo — Home</PageTitle>

<div class="intro">
    <h1>BlazorCsvExporter</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        A reusable <strong>CSV export component</strong> for Blazor Server and Blazor Web App (.NET 8).
    </p>

    <p>
        Export any <code>IEnumerable&lt;T&gt;</code> to a CSV file directly from your Blazor pages —
        configurable, lightweight, and dependency-free.
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>✔️ Export any list or query to CSV</li>
        <li>✔️ Choose delimiter and header</li>
        <li>✔️ Select which properties to include</li>
    </ul>

    <NavLink href="/export-demo" class="btn-primary">
        Try the Demo →
    </NavLink>
</div>
